sequenceDiagram
    participant Node
    participant NS as Network Server
    
    Note over Node, NS: AppEUI, DevEUI, AppKey (Pre-provisioned)
    Node->>NS: Join Request (DevEUI, AppEUI, MIC)
    Note over NS: Verifies MIC using AppKey
    Note over NS: Generates DevAddr, NwkSKey, AppSKey
    NS-->>Node: Join Accept (Encrypted with AppKey)
    Note over Node: Derives NwkSKey, AppSKey, DevAddr
    Note over Node, NS: Session established
    Node->>NS: Data Uplink (Encrypted with AppSKey, signed with NwkSKey)
